# 🎨 High-Fidelity UI Design – Digital Talent Management System  

## 💻 Overview  
The high-fidelity UI design focuses on delivering a **complete, polished, and production-ready interface** for the Digital Talent Management System. It incorporates visual design, branding, and usability across all user roles and platforms.

---

## 🎯 Design Goals  
- Deliver a **visually consistent and professional interface**  
- Ensure **role-based user experience** for all users  
- Improve **usability and interaction clarity**  
- Maintain **design consistency across web and mobile**  

---

## 👥 User Roles Covered  

- **HR Admin** → Full system control and management  
- **Team Manager** → Task assignment and team monitoring  
- **Employee** → Task execution and personal updates  

